  "Description": {
    "English": "A complex arrangement of membranes and lens, fused atop a high-energy laser array. Incineration awaits those that meet their stare.<br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> request the eyes gaze upon nearby targets.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种膜和透镜的复杂排列，融合在一个高能激光阵列上。焚化等待着那些与他们目光相遇的人。<br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>请求眼睛注视附近的目标。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "由鏡頭和黏膜組合而成的複雜結構，融合在高能雷射陣列上方。只要和這雙眼睛四目相交，就會被燒成灰燼。<br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 請求眼睛看向附近的目標。"
  },
  "Teach": true,
  "HintStart": "",
  "HintEnd": {
    "English": "Switch Weapon Mode by pressing <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span><br>Fire Weapons with <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切换武器模式<br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 用武器开火",
    "TencentChinese": "按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切换武器模式<br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 用武器开火",
    "TraditionalChinese": "按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPCYCLEWEAPON</span> 切換武器模式<br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 發射武器"
  },
